{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7b64191b97","title":"王力关锋就新华总社请示报告给陈伯达康生江青等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7165dbc97d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"7b64191b97"}],"tags":[{"id":"00506c3c84","name":"关锋","type":"人物"},{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"268718f23b","name":"新闻广播和出版","type":"主题"},{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4e86219feb","name":"关锋"},{"id":"fa147b61e7","name":"王力"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6ebbf93884","type":"title","text":"王力关锋就新华总社请示报告给陈伯达康生江青等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"22af1faecd","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达、康生、江青、本禹、文元同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"fedd424038","type":"paragraph","text":"在无产阶级文化大革命中，新华社许多地方分社的记者，在大风大浪中经受考验，坚定地站在毛主席的无产阶级革命路线一边，站在左派群众一边，出生入死，坐监狱，被绑架，向中央反映了真实情况。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"ec305e29aa","type":"paragraph","text":"为了表扬这批战士，在宣传战线上树立拥护毛泽东思想的标兵，我们建议召开一个无产阶级革命派新闻战士会议。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"61db262154","type":"paragraph","text":"一、八月下旬召开。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"41e7500172","type":"paragraph","text":"二、文革小组同志，准备集体接见一次。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"088dd12bb9","type":"paragraph","text":"三、登报支持他们，他们中许多人还受打击。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"c711b76bc8","type":"paragraph","text":"四、新华社提出一个初步方案，办事组和×××需作审查一下，请批示。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"41f64af801","type":"paragraph","text":"王力、关锋","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7b64191b97"},{"id":"a9118659ae","type":"paragraph","t